oracle.pg.common.messages

Interface MesgConsts

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    OracleMessageConstants
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphLoader, Message, NoSQLCommon, OracleCommonIteratorBase, OracleCommonIteratorImpl, OracleDataLoaderUtils, OracleEdge, OracleEdgeFilterIteratorImpl, OracleEdgeIteratorImpl, OracleElementIteratorImpl, OraclePropertyGraph, OraclePropertyGraphBase, OraclePropertyGraphDataLoader, OraclePropertyGraphUtils, OraclePropertyGraphUtilsBase, OracleTinkerpop30EdgeIteratorImpl, OracleTinkerpop30VertexIteratorImpl, OracleVertexFilterIteratorImpl, OracleVertexIteratorImpl, SolrVertexIndex

    public interface MesgConsts
    This interface defines the message constants.
